OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,FThe Association of Jersey Charities is
OL,7,Fasking the island's next set of
OL,8,Fpoliticians to introduce a formal
OL,9,Fcommissioning model for charity
OL,10,Fgrants, which would provide stable,
OL,11,Fmulti-year funding.
OL,13,FCharities in the Bailiwick are
OL,14,Fcurrently given variable one-off
OL,15,Fgrants, which typically last for a
OL,16,Fyear at a time.
OL,18,FThis means they cannot plan ahead -
OL,19,Fgiven the unpredictable and variable
OL,20,Flevels of government funding they
OL,21,Freceive.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,FThe Association is also asking
OL,7,Fcandidates standing in the upcoming
OL,8,FJune election to pledge to recognise
OL,9,Fcharities as strategic partners in
OL,10,Fpolicymaking and service delivery.
OL,12,FRobert Surcouf, the Association's
OL,13,Fchair, explains: "Currently, certain
OL,14,Fcharities go through a procurement
OL,15,Fwhere they are providing services that
OL,16,Fare vital to the island, and they tend
OL,17,Fto be very cost-effective, trusted
OL,18,Fproviders - and the government
OL,19,Fprovides funding.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,F"But they're only providing the
OL,7,Ffunding as a one-year basis and the
OL,8,Fcharity has to reapply every year, the
OL,9,Fgovernment has to reassess it.
OL,11,F"We think it would be far better if
OL,12,Fthat was a multi-year position -
OL,13,Fobviously there's KPIs (Key
OL,14,FPerformance Indicators) and the
OL,15,Fcharities are used to providing that
OL,16,Finformation - but it would give them
OL,17,Fmore certainty to be able to plan."
OL,26,@uD@XpmvD@Wpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,FHe says it is not all charities that
OL,7,Fare asking for more, only those
OL,8,Fproviding key services on behalf of
OL,9,Fthe States such as healthcare services
OL,10,Fand homelessness support.
OL,12,FBrighter Futures is one of those
OL,13,Fcharities: providing early support for
OL,14,Fstruggling families through childcare
OL,15,Fgroups, personal development
OL,16,Fprogrammes, and one-to-one targeted
OL,17,Fcounselling.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,FThey receive referrals from government
OL,7,Fagencies - such as health visitors,
OL,8,Fsocial workers, and the children's
OL,9,Fservice - and support a wide number of
OL,10,Fstate bodies.
OL,12,FHowever, Fiona Brennan, the charity's
OL,13,FCEO, says that forecasting the
OL,14,Fcharity's future at present is
OL,15,Fimpossible.
OL,17,FShe explains: "Without sustainable
OL,18,Ffunding, we can't plan or grow, and it
OL,19,Fmeans we're very restricted in what we
OL,20,Fcan offer.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,F"What we need now, is we need our
OL,7,Fpoliticians to be brave.
OL,9,F"Brighter Futures would have folded
OL,10,Fmany years ago if we didn't have a
OL,11,Fwide number of private and corporate
OL,12,Fdonors on the island, because
OL,13,Fgovernment funding has been so little.
OL,15,F"However, if they could give us a
OL,16,Fcommissioning model for three years,
OL,17,Fand a reasonable amount of financial
OL,18,Fsupport, we can continue to grow our
OL,19,Fservices and offer social and economic
OL,20,Fvalue to Jersey for years to come."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,FCiara O'Keeffe turned to Brighter
OL,7,FFutures for support after becoming a
OL,8,Fparent, and believes the charity's
OL,9,Fservices are "essential" in Jersey.
OL,11,FShe says: "I had quite a traumatic
OL,12,Fbirth with my first son, and Brighter
OL,13,FFutures put me in touch with another
OL,14,Fagency who helped me fully understand
OL,15,Fand process what had happened.
OL,17,F"They've changed my life by helping me
OL,18,Fhave access to that service, and I now
OL,19,Fhave a very strong relationship with
OL,20,Fmy son.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,F"Brighter Futures should definitely be
OL,7,Frecognised as an essential public
OL,8,Fservice - they're amazing and need to
OL,9,Fbe recognised for what they do."
OL,11,FIn March, the island's Community
OL,12,FFoundation found that charities
OL,13,Fproviding healthcare services alone
OL,14,Fdelivered around #6.2 million in net
OL,15,Fsavings for the Government in 2024,
OL,16,Fand added an estimated #137.4 million
OL,17,Fin economic and social value.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,FFiona believes this establishes a
OL,7,Ffinancial case, as well as a moral
OL,8,Fone, for introducing a sustainable
OL,9,Ffunding model.
OL,11,FShe adds: "Surely, common sense says
OL,12,Fthat if you invest in these charities
OL,13,Fnow, in the long term you will be able
OL,14,Fto save the hard-earned money of the
OL,15,Fpeople of Jersey.
OL,17,F"The most we've ever had is 30% of our
OL,18,Ffunding - this year we have 8.7% from
OL,19,Fthe Government, and it will cost us
OL,20,Fover #1 million to offer our services
OL,21,Ffor families in Jersey for free.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1776942175
OL,3,CJersey charities call for more
OL,4,Csustainable funding
OL,6,F"For us to continue to offer the
OL,7,Fservices, if we didn't get government
OL,8,Fsupport, would be next to impossible."
OL,10,FThe Association of Jersey Charities is
OL,11,Falso asking election candidates to
OL,12,Fpledge they will consult the third
OL,13,Fsector in the early stage of forming
OL,14,Fpolicies which affect the communities
OL,15,Fthey serve, ensure fair commissioning
OL,16,Fand procurement processes, and invest
OL,17,Fin the long-term strength and
OL,18,Fsustainability of Jersey's charitable
OL,19,Fsector.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
